public enum WebApiMethodType
extends java.lang.Enum<WebApiMethodType>

The Zend Server Web API is intended to allow automation of the management and deployment of Zend Server and Zend Server Cluster Manager, and allow integration with other Zend or 3rd party software.
Each registered service method is represented by its name and request and response properties

Author:
Roy, 2011
See Also:
IRequest, IResponseData
